{"tid":445908,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又違反聯合聲] 中國教育部長指港獨關教育事：老師首先要愛國","createTime":"2017-10-23T23:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T07:38:45.000Z","uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c7dbdcbe26143097268d47aecbe8a0d6af08994d","tid":445908,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T23:54:33.000Z","msg":"在北京出席十九大會議的教育部長陳寶生接受港台訪問時直指，近期在香港出現的港獨思潮，與教育當然有關，不利香港繁榮穩定，特區政府有責任推行國民教育。陳寶生聲稱不評論出現港獨思潮是否特區政府回歸後在教育方面做得不好，「答案每一個香港人自有判斷&hellip;&hellip;心知肚明」，而特區政府的國教課程是否跟隨內地的愛國教育課程，由特區政府自行決定。<br />\n<br />\n陳寶生認為，國教課程應要把中華民族五千年至中共建國的偉大歷程告訴香港青年人，令他們認同自己是中國人，增加民族自豪感。<br />\n<br />\n陳寶生強調，國民教育是基本教育，要推動國民教育，老師是關鍵，老師要先認同和愛國家，特區政府亦應讓老師團體正確認識國情，「他們首先得愛這個國家、認同這個國家，增加民族自豪感，和祖國一起享受我們發展的成果」。被問到會否擔心在香港推國教遇阻力，陳寶生指一個堅強的政府要履行執政職責，政府要辦的事情是有責任和能力去辦到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171023/57365973\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171023%2F57365973&d=u9KxolH6fjab1lnHyOyfZfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=58ca71af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171023%2F57365973&h=3c236302\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171023/57365973</a>"},{"pid":"1ce06f4f863d817ae32ec26228bc260531783e60","tid":445908,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T23:56:36.000Z","msg":"聽聞支那話聯合聲明已失效？"},{"pid":"ee8e66fd70d3ab773dfd1c8cb6e9b0a9f27204e8","tid":445908,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T23:56:50.000Z","msg":"The Hong Kong Special Administrative Region Government shall on its own decide policies in the fields of culture, education, science and technology, including policies regarding the educational system and its administration, the language of instruction, the allocation of funds, the examination system, the system of academic awards and the recognition of educational and technological qualifications. Institutions of all kinds, including those run by religious and community organisations, may retain their autonomy.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cmab.gov.hk/en/issues/jd3b.htm#educat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmab.gov.hk%2Fen%2Fissues%2Fjd3b.htm%23educat&d=u9KxolH6fjab1lnHyOyfZfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=890623f4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cmab.gov.hk/en/issues/jd3b.htm#educat</a>"},{"pid":"3a9928fb1144053932a3ab221200dfd264ba4807","tid":445908,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T23:57:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽聞支那話聯合聲明已失效？</blockquote><br />\n之後有反過口嘅(技術上)"},{"pid":"7153d8698df347ac565b6719da16d17a466ae2d4","tid":445908,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:00:39.000Z","msg":"教師都要洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2faff2659bd7fdd9d9a33ab4183511f67ace29","tid":445908,"uid":139349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:24:15.000Z","msg":"試著不說，聯合聲明<br />\n試著說，賣國條約"},{"pid":"8c8f34bffb4d7f00a44cd32e7cfd3b89e851367b","tid":445908,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:31:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教師都要洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所有香港人，中國都想洗啦"},{"pid":"ba8f815dd44929e5fb44931286da83d8873ffcd4","tid":445908,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T02:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be9819425ec27d831a80856dd589b075f9160d7","tid":445908,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T02:19:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">[突發0950]<br />\n五毛三色貓狂推失敗主義post</span>"},{"pid":"a57c55667507823b7d43f6df8812dcaa2cd5420f","tid":445908,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike